---
---

<section
  id="servicios"
  class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-white"
  aria-labelledby="servicios-title"
>
  <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 max-w-[700px] mx-auto">
      <span class="inline-block text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-primary mb-2 px-3 py-1 bg-primary/10 rounded-full">
        Nuestros Servicios
      </span>
      <h2 id="servicios-title" class="animate-on-scroll text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">
        Lo que hacemos
      </h2>
      <p class="animate-on-scroll text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
        Diseño, fabricación e instalación para espacios comerciales y públicos
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="services-grid grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <article class="group animate-on-scroll bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-[rgba(217,188,74,0.03)] rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-md hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-[0_20px_40px_rgba(217,188,74,0.1)] transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 border border-transparent hover:border-primary/20 border-t-4 border-t-primary focus-within:ring-2 focus-within:ring-primary/50">
        <div class="service-icon w-20 h-20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-foreground text-3xl bg-primary shadow-[0_4px_12px_rgba(217,188,74,0.3)] group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-store" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">
          Centros Comerciales
        </h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
          Transformamos plazas y malls en destinos atractivos con decoraciones temáticas que generan tráfico y engagement.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="group animate-on-scroll bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-[rgba(217,188,74,0.03)] rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-md hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-[0_20px_40px_rgba(217,188,74,0.1)] transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 border border-transparent hover:border-primary/20 border-t-4 border-t-primary focus-within:ring-2 focus-within:ring-primary/50">
        <div class="service-icon w-20 h-20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-foreground text-3xl bg-primary shadow-[0_4px_12px_rgba(217,188,74,0.3)] group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-tree-city" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">
          Plazas y Espacios Públicos
        </h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
          Decoramos explanadas, plazas y zonas públicas para crear espacios que la comunidad disfrute y comparta.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="group animate-on-scroll bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-[rgba(217,188,74,0.03)] rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-md hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-[0_20px_40px_rgba(217,188,74,0.1)] transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 border border-transparent hover:border-primary/20 border-t-4 border-t-primary focus-within:ring-2 focus-within:ring-primary/50">
        <div class="service-icon w-20 h-20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-foreground text-3xl bg-primary shadow-[0_4px_12px_rgba(217,188,74,0.3)] group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-days" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">
          Temporadas y Festividades
        </h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
          Desde Reyes Magos hasta Navidad: diseñamos, fabricamos e instalamos decoraciones temáticas para cada festividad del año.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="group animate-on-scroll bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-[rgba(217,188,74,0.03)] rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-md hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-[0_20px_40px_rgba(217,188,74,0.1)] transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 border border-transparent hover:border-primary/20 border-t-4 border-t-primary focus-within:ring-2 focus-within:ring-primary/50">
        <div class="service-icon w-20 h-20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-foreground text-3xl bg-primary shadow-[0_4px_12px_rgba(217,188,74,0.3)] group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-boxes-packing" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">
          Servicio Llave en Mano
        </h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
          Diseño, fabricación, montaje, mantenimiento, desmontaje, embalaje profesional y organización en bodega. Un solo proveedor, cero preocupaciones.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
